    <item>
      <title>人工智能担忧导致亚洲股市下跌，美元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对人工智能公司估值过高的担忧重创美国股市，亚洲股市多数下跌。美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示希望提高普遍关税，美元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 22:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将注入 180 亿美元现金以填补巨大的流动性缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行计划向国内金融系统注入近 180 亿美元，加大力度缓解现金短缺问题。印度现金短缺问题达到十多年来的最高水平，一些人认为这损害了亚洲第三大经济体的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/india-central-bank-takes-steps-to-boost-cash-via-bond-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 12:27:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人民币限制宽松之际，中国人民银行通过新工具注入创纪录流动性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/pboc-injects-record-liquidity-using-its-new-tool-delays-rrr-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行一月份通过新工具向金融系统注入了创纪录数量的现金，推迟了更多引人注目的政策放松，因为其优先考虑稳定人民币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/pboc-injects-record-liquidity-using-its-new-tool-delays-rrr-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 10:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
